# Data files
data/raw/*
!data/raw/HB 300 CD 1.txt
!data/raw/vetoes/
# Draft bill texts are the source-of-truth inputs for the draft-compare JSONs;
# track them so the comparison pipeline is reproducible from a fresh clone.
# (HB1800_CD1.txt also carries hand-applied corrections for markup the RTF→text
#  conversion dropped — see commit 08c5f83.)
!data/raw/drafts/
# County budget source files (Honolulu Socrata JSON, county ordinance PDFs).
# Committed so scripts/process_county_budgets.py runs offline from a fresh
# clone, mirroring the HB300 convention above.
!data/raw/counties/
data/processed/*
!data/processed/budget_parsed*.csv
!data/processed/budget_allocations*.csv
!data/processed/department_descriptions.json
!data/processed/counties/
data/output/*
!data/output/departmental_reports/

